Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: SMUTHI
Version: 0.1
Summary: Light scattering by multiple particles in thin-film systems
Home-page: https://gitlab.com/AmosEgel/smuthi
Author: Amos Egel
Author-email: amos.egel@kit.edu
License: MIT
Description: SMUTHI allows to simulate light scattering by multiple particles near (or between) planar interfaces. It is based on the T-matrix method for the single particle scattering, and on the scattering-matrix method for the propagation through the layered medium.
Platform: UNKNOWN
